Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,VICTORY OR ANNIHILATION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a Darkling could be this resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter me. I'm just a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A cowardly, small, ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who speak like that\Nare often dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are far more dangerous\Nthan you let on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it from the first time we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you keep using magic\Neven though I keep reflecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would assume you have some sort of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the most difficult enemy\NI've ever faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone I've ever fought\Nassumed I was just a scrub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That always let me catch them off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using spells to find\Nan opening in my defenses aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have one spell\Nthat can defeat me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and use it. That Medoroa spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. If you reflect\Nmy Medoroa then it'll really be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving you\Nwhat you want so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A IO spell. Futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just reflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Counter and cancel it out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Extend, Black Rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rod, into fork spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did it! I got the mirror off\Nand immobilized them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so calm?! Struggle more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You completely exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To hide such a powerful ace\Nup your sleeve all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have won if it wasn't\Nmy right arm you pinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}Lightning Buster!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't the only one\Nwith an ace up your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lightning Buster from my right arm\Nis as powerful as a Ionazun spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Hym's Heat Knuckle, it requires\Nphysical contact to work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard bone shatter.\NYou're beyond help now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for heading to the next battle\Nwithout offering proper rites.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My worthy adversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! How are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... a Behoma spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been so resilient because you've\Nbeen healing yourself this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a Sage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not. I ain't no Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't no Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, Mentor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use attack and healing\Nand all sorts of types of spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that not make you a Sage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds so pompous and doesn't fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it lacks impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came up with an awesome title\Nthat would make everybody fear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The title of the single most\Npowerful spell-caster in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daimadoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to call me anything,\Ncall me the Daimadoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, the Daimadoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, that doesn't seem\Nfar off the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you attain such a spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My mentor already made me bind\Nwith almost every spell there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just suddenly was able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaining power at the moment\Nyou most hate yourself is pretty ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been\Nmore ashamed of myself before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul is what awakened that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul can enhance the body\Nbeyond its limits. That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This soul that Lord Hadorra gave me\Nis my greatest pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,unfortunately, that doesn't\Ngive you any advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing will only lengthen our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All the better for me, since I'm trying to\Nbuy time for Lord Hadorra and Dai's duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be... so sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Medoroa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize\NI won't just let you hit me with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it's the only spell\Nthat'll work on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It all comes down to this Medoroa spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an opponent worth respecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll match that sense of duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Dai as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could try to buy time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've gained my interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Grand Sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up! That sort of movement speed\Nwill never catch me off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the goddess of victory\Ndoes not smile for you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My goddess doesn't smile for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She slaps me across the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No you're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own weapon will send you\Nto the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to offer the same line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Medoroa will send you\Nto the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He is about to be annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't been annihilated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I win the game of deception!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Medoroa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MEDOROA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.60,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}LIGHTNING BUSTER{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that first spell... wasn't Medoroa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I adjusted my Magic Power\Nand disguised a Begirama spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I intentionally let myself get hit...\Nto catch you off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a satisfying fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadorra will not blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall not forget your name,\NDaimadoshi Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither, Knight Sigma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to\Nyour goddess who slaps you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a brilliant flash from Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That light is from Popp's Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Disciples of Aban are fighting well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's his Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't let them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Howl, Inferno!{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come to help?\NDid you really have no faith in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally, finally got to say it\Nto your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That last confession was just the worst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're wondering why\NI'm choosing to say this here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say it properly\Nbefore the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you were uncomfortable\Nwith how things stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to hear my answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just say your piece\Nand end things there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You never do beat around the bush, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I have to fall in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've always been a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now I'm terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared you're not interested in me\Nor that you really love Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even back with the Minakator spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared of\Ngetting wounded or even dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be left out of the group...\NThat scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have Dai or you with me,\NI'd still be worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When my Insignia didn't glow, I should've\Njust come out and asked for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someone told me\NI'm not worthy to be among you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That fear kept me silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it was Master Aban\Nwho kept it from glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saying "I won't have any student\Nof mine chickening out like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry, Maam. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I should accept whatever's coming to me\Nor I'll never be able to face Meruru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I guess I'm\Nthe Disciple of Courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I go astray, you wake me up\Nand put me back on the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that quality of yours that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How I... feel about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought\Nyou were in love with Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I love Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong, but so alone,\Nand I'm always worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the same goes for you, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always afraid to let you out of\Nmy sight. You're like a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A little brother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When I learned you're in love with me\NI was conflicted at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm grateful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not ready to give you an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized something in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I never actually knew what real love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy and Meruru and Albinass were all\Nwilling to die for the people they loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To truly love someone\Nis a fierce and powerful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm capable of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I never considered how to see others\Nor how others saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've been hurt and suffered\Nnumerous times because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give an answer to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'll allow it,\Nwill you give me a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we'll survive this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if we do manage to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that then I'll be able\Nto look at you as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm able to love you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I've seen you grow so much\Nthrough your battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's fight for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The future...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if I'll be able to love you\Nas a man when it's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may love Hyunckel instead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I know I'll be able to become\Nsomeone I wasn't before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for the future, let's work together\Nand overcome this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best I can offer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it... enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you. That answer\Nwas far more than I deserve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... I'm so glad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fell in love with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if the Dark King ends up killing us,\Nthen that's that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... can I have an advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! Fooled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I'm not brave enough to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you really closed your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be you might actually\Nhave feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's win this. I want to see that future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's the one\Nwhere I get shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Maam! You're both okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your fight\Nwith Sigma was a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Half of this is from Maam, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing here?\NWhere are Dai and Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what? I can't see them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a huge swirl of sheer heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp and Maam arrive to help Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Hadorra's clash\Nrivals one from legends of the Underworld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is one that none may interrupt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's Aban Strash\Nor Hadorra's Ultra Combustion Slash...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The duel between the two\Nnears its conclusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Battle of True Dragons"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
